title: Efficient Export Customs Clearance
description: In 2023, Croatia achieved an average time of just 1.1 days to clear exports through customs, making it one of the fastest in the world.

title: Robust Institutional Infrastructure for Insolvency
description: Croatia scored 91.67 in 2024 for the quality of its institutional and operational infrastructure for judicial insolvency proceedings, indicating a strong framework.

title: High Tuberculosis Case Detection Rate
description: In 2023, Croatia reported a tuberculosis case detection rate of 190%, suggesting potential over-reporting or data discrepancies.
